ByteHTTPD Alpha!
V0.0.2
http://bytepub.us/httpd

All additions to the code are welcome!
This code is based on the IBM nweb tutorial on their website. 

To run ByteHTTPD
# ./bytehttpd 80 /path/to/www/folder

